# Receiver Endpoint

The receiver endpoint where GOV.UK One Login Transmitter will send signals realated to user activity. 

The transmitter will make the following request 

```bash
curl --request POST \
  --url https://your.service.gov.uk/oauth/token \
  --header 'accept: application/json' \
  --header 'authorization: Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN' \
  --header 'content-type: application/secevent+jwt' \
  --data PAYLOAD
```
The payload is a [Security Event Token][external.security-event-token]

